1) geometry package can help you adjust the margins easily
    \usepackage[left=2cm,top=1cm,bottom=2cm,right=3cm,nohead,nofoot]{geometry}
   For actual usage, see "8th_sem_seminar_report" 
    
    
2) titlesec package can let you adjust the font size of chapter headings easily
    \titleformat{\chapter}{\bf\huge}{\thechapter}{1em}{}
    \titleformat{name of section command}{formatting}{label: in my case the chap    ter counter}{spacing between text and label}{code to go after text}    
